{'question': 'How do I run diagnostics on an LG dishwasher?', 'response': '1. Unplug the dishwasher or disconnect power, then perform the "Service Mode Test" on page 2-3 of your user manual. This test checks for incoming and outgoing power to and from the control board, ensuring proper voltages are present at the outlet or direct connect cable. If any issues are detected, follow the appropriate troubleshooting steps in your manual based on the error codes generated during the test.', 'expected_keywords': [], 'expected_sources': [], 'latency_s': 4.181674957275391}
